title: Did Dr. Fuse say that he was "nothing to worry'about " COVID-19?
subtitle: The accusations that Dr. Anthony Faucy said he was "safe" to go to cinema and sports in late February 2020 ignored the main facts about the outbreak of the Corona virus at the time.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: "There's nothing to worry about" said Dr. Anthony Faucy in late February 2020 regarding COVID-19 and was "safe" to do things like go to the movies and gym.
